[SPEAKER_00] Mi bi ti dali ove mali, gledamo.

583
00:47:07,219 --> 00:47:07,780
[SPEAKER_00] Da.

584
00:47:07,780 --> 00:47:10,260
[SPEAKER_00] Kako, četiri bi stale. Četiri.

585
00:47:10,260 --> 00:47:11,260
[SPEAKER_01] Četiri sarme.

586
00:47:11,260 --> 00:47:19,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ali možemo javno pozvati, koji ima veći lonac ekipa našoj olimpijašiciji, već ja trakiram jabate.

587
00:47:19,280 --> 00:47:20,099
[SPEAKER_00] Može, može.

588
00:47:20,099 --> 00:47:22,599
[SPEAKER_00] Od vode, da, ovo što stoji tu.

589
00:47:22,599 --> 00:47:23,619
[SPEAKER_00] Može. Ovo koju ne pijemo, da.

590
00:47:24,179 --> 00:47:24,619
[SPEAKER_00] Ništa.

591
00:47:24,619 --> 00:47:28,480
[SPEAKER_00] Tebi, tvoji obitelji, želim puno uspjeha u 2025.

592
00:47:28,480 --> 00:47:33,739
[SPEAKER_00] Zdravlja, medalja, bodova, turnira, šta god si sama zaželiš.

593
00:47:33,739 --> 00:47:36,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ja si sve to isto želim. Hvala.

594
00:47:36,659 --> 00:47:39,719
[SPEAKER_00] Hvala ti još jednom i viš, idemo na kavu, kak velimo.

595
00:47:39,719 --> 00:47:40,139
[SPEAKER_01] Idemo.

596
00:47:40,139 --> 00:47:40,599
[SPEAKER_01] Idemo.

597
00:47:40,599 --> 00:47:41,599
[SPEAKER_00] Ekipa, bok.

598
00:47:41,599 --> 00:47:42,360
[SPEAKER_01] Vakić.

599
00:47:46,360 --> 00:48:10,739
[UNKNOWN] Hvala ti još jednom i viš, idemo na kavu, kak velimo.

